# Start
  "test": "jest"   - in package.json, test script
  npm test (execute in terminal)

# Dependencies
  npm init -y      - install nodepackages, package json  
  npm i -D jest    - install as dev-dependence Jest
  npm i axios      - install axios for http request

# Fake API for Tests
  https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com

# Jest WatchMode
    (npm run testwatch)
 		"testwatch": "jest --watchAll"    - terminal options for tests
      - only failed test
      - run tests related to changed files
      - by a filename regex pattern
      - by a test name regex pattern
      - quit watch WatchMode
      - trigger a test run